Class SAMMFileInfoFilter

      • mnThumbnailSamplingSize

        public int mnThumbnailSamplingSize
        The desired sampling size(width or height) of the thumbnail(The aspect ratio is not changed) This size option is to load thumbnail fast with maintaining aspect ratio, and the thumbnail width or height may not same as the sample size.
        If the sampling size <= 0, the extracted thumbnail has original size.
        Since:
        S-Pen SDK 2.2, SAMM Library 1.5

      • mnThumbnailScalingWidth

        public int mnThumbnailScalingWidth
        The scaling width of the extracted thumbnail.
        If the scaling width <= 0, the size of extracted thumbnail depends on mnThumbnailMaxSize.
        Since:
        S-Pen SDK 2.2, SAMM Library 1.5

      • mnThumbnailScalingHeight
